{"tid":49801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【禁錮驚魂】網民「起錯底」 姓梁青年無辜被當淫賊","createTime":"2016-12-22T03:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T06:21:29.000Z","uid":48093,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87aafba9aea5a842dc0fd2339bedc7f31a453f39","tid":49801,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161222/large/1482375890_76ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161222%2Flarge%2F1482375890_76ed.jpg&h=71bd811c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人在網上圖文並茂貼「禁錮出租女友」文章，惹起網友不安並有多人報警，警方昨晚拘捕一名22歲姓賴青年，涉嫌有犯罪或不誠實意圖而取用電腦及浪費警力。然而，在涉案青年被捕前，有網民卻對這名「淫賊」進行「大起底」，結果「起錯底」，並將一名姓梁青年的個人資料放上網，令無辜青年一度被指是禁錮少女的變態淫賊。<br />\n<br />\n被誤當淫賊的姓梁青年的名字、facebook、電話及母校等資料遭披露，他向《蘋果》指對事件大感錯愕，稱並「有啲擔心」遭人抨擊，亦擔心影響日後工作及母校校譽，幸警方拉人及早查出真相，證實自己非涉案人，他希望有關網民可以盡快將其個人資料刪除。<br />\n<br />\n梁指，自己較少瀏覽網上論壇，對一般「起底」、「公審」之事較少留意，認為事主若犯錯要承擔責任，但自己一向不會落井下石。"},{"pid":"908cd57973ad5530011165a52137aa8a4732957d","tid":49801,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:23:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"615398325f397496eb760ef1a241decd75f9e40c","tid":49801,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:35:58.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac24f9e0e0a0dc7db45d9c202056df2fc5b6b86","tid":49801,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:16:46.000Z","msg":"邊條仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f848fb201d2e67374e0990f00fddbb561bf43bdf","tid":49801,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:44:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c9c4e7baaf9466e9fbff02a3a68660